1-https://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp 2-Since Java Development Kit (JDK) 6.2 isn't there anymore I click on IDK 6.3 3-I click on "[u]Windows Online Installation, Multi-language[/u]" and download [IMG]http://i180.photobucket.com/albums/x303/mystickid2k6/Javastarting.jpg[/img] Ok these are my first 2 attempts to try and download it: [IMG]http://i180.photobucket.com/albums/x303/mystickid2k6/SunTMDownloadManager.jpg[/img] I click start and this is what happens...I would really appreciate the help from you peole and I would give rep++ now that I can thanks :D
